bilingual.source: An engine drives the wheels on the road.
bilingual.target: 发动机驱动车轮在路上行驶。

bilingual.source: Engine oil is very important for the engine's operation.
bilingual.target: 机油对发动机的运行非常重要。
这台发动机的冲程很长。

bilingual.source: The engine has a lot of torque.
bilingual.target: 这个发动机的转矩很大。
这个发动机有四个气缸。

list.abstract: engine作n.时是指发动机，引擎；作vt.时是指给…安装发动机。其过去分词为engined、第三人称单数为engines。
《ENGINE》(エンジン)，是日本富士电视台于2005年4月18日到6月27日播放的日本电视剧。由井上由美子编剧，木村拓哉、小雪等人主演。 该剧讲述了一位个性率真的过气赛车手与12个年纪不同的孤儿院孩子，以及一位美丽女老师的故事。

yingyinNormal.en: Which engine? He lost thrust in both engines, he said.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哪台发动机？他说2台发动机都停车了。

yingyinNormal.en: You show me the left engine, I'll show you dead birds and no power.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你把左翼发动机找来，我就给你看死鸟和停车的痕迹。

yingyinNormal.en: Riding in the pedalo on a sunny lake. Daddy is the engine, I hope he doesn't break.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在洒满阳光的湖上划着船，爸爸是发动机，我希望他不会坏掉。

yingyinNormal.en: The evidence shows that the left engine was at idle or sub-idle immediately following the bird strike.
yingyinNormal.zh: 记录显示就在鸟击过后，左翼发动机在空转或次空转状态。

yingyinNormal.en: Gentlemen, I want to inform you that the left engine has been recovered. We just received a comprehensive report.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两位我想告知你们，左翼发动机已被捞出，我们刚收到详细调查报告。

yingyinNormal.en: The left engine might have still been idling. And the Airbus simulations say I could've made it back to LaGuardia safely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 左翼发动机有可能一直在空转，而且空客的模拟显示，我可以安全返回拉瓜迪亚机场。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, you need to return to LaGuardia? Turn left heading 2-2-0. 2-2-0. Which engine did you lose? Both. Both engines.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的，你需要返回拉瓜迪亚？左转航向220。航向220。哪台发动机停车？双发，双发停车。

yingyinNormal.en: The left engine was lost in the crash due to excessive damage on touchdown. But we can circle back to that later. Let's just assume that it was, as you say, a dual engine loss due to bird strike.
yingyinNormal.zh: 左翼发动机在坠机过程中，因水面撞击而丢失，不过我们可以以后再研究这个问题，我们就先假定你说的是事实因鸟击造成双发停车。

yingyinNormal.en: He switched on the APU immediately after engine rollback. According to Airbus, that's the 15th thing on the list to do. Fifteenth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 发动机刚减速，他就打开了辅助动力装置，而根据空客的检查单，那是要做的第15件事，第15件。

yingyinNormal.en: There was extensive damage to both the guide vanes and fan blades of the engine. Five compressor blades were fractured and eight variable guide vanes missing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 发动机上的导流叶片和风扇叶片都受到了大面积损伤，5个压缩机叶片断裂，还有8个可变导流叶片丢失。

yingyinNormal.en: Your union has been advised. ACARS data relayed that the left engine continued to turn throughout the flight. Then the ACARS data is wrong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们的工会已被告知，飞机通信寻址与报告系统的传输数据显示，左翼发动机在整个飞行期间一直在转动。那飞机通信寻址与报告系统的数据错了。

yingyinNormal.en: The engine room of Paris is La Defense.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拉德芳斯区是巴黎的核心区域。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy, can we see the fire engine? Yes. Oh, goodie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，我们能去看看消防联盟吗？当然！噢，太好啦！

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, the sailing boat does have an engine. Full sail.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，帆船上有引擎。全速前进！

yingyinNormal.en: The Fire Engine
yingyinNormal.zh: 消防车

yingyinNormal.en: Swim faster, Daddy. Stop the engine. What's he saying? Stop the engine. Daddy says, stop the engine. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 游快一点，爸爸。要把引擎关掉。他在说什么？把引擎关掉。爸爸他说，把引擎关掉。

yingyinNormal.en: It's not moving. No, how do we start the engine? You are the engine, Daddy Pig, you have to paddle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这没有动。我们如何发动引擎？哈哈哈，你就是引擎，猪爸爸，你要脚踩。

yingyinNormal.en: The Check Engine light is fine. It's still blinking away. It's the stupid engine that stopped working.
yingyinNormal.zh: 引擎检修灯还好着呢，现在还闪呢，是那个可恶的引擎罢工了。

yingyinNormal.en: This is Miss. Rabbit's fire station. Hello, Peppa and George. Come and see the fire engine. Fire engine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里是兔小姐的消防站。你们好啊，佩奇和乔治。进来看看消防车吧。消防车！

yingyinNormal.en: We simply pour the oil into the engine and oh… What's wrong? There's nothing in here. The engine's gone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们只要把这桶汽油倒到油箱里，然后，噢。怎么了？这里面什么也没有，引擎消失了。

examination_example.sentence: Technology—first fire and stone tools and later farming, the steam <highlight>engine</highlight>, fossil fuels and nuclear power—has allowed us to alter the natural world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 正如神话中所说，技术首先是火和石器，然后是种植、蒸汽机、化石燃料和核能，使我们能够改变自然世界。

examination_example.sentence: New electric <highlight>engines</highlight> coupled with artificial intelligence and autonomous systems will contribute to a more efficient, integrated transport system.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 新的电动发动机加上人工智能和自动系统将有助于建立一个更高效、更一体化的运输系统。

examination_example.sentence: The partnership benefits both sides by allowing unconventional partners to work together, like, an <highlight>engine</highlight> firm with an accessory one.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种合作关系允许非传统的合作伙伴一起工作，比如一家发动机公司和一家配件公司，这对双方都有利。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 马可尼与今天的社交媒体搜索引擎有着直接的联系。
